title: Zephyr - Sunset ride (1972)
description:
Cool american poprock with a little bit of country and a tad jazz in the mix. Singer sounds a bit like Janis Joplin. This band used to play with famous guitarplayer Tommy Brolin, but broke up with him, and this record is what came out after the breakup. Very good, in my opinion.
